"questions, feel free to contact us at <t t-out=\"object.company_id.email\">."
"</t></div><br/><div>Warm regards, </div><div>The <t t-"
"out=\"object.company_id.name\"> team </t></div><div><t t-"
"out=\"object.company_id.email\"> | <t t-out=\"object.company_id.phone\"/></"
"t></div>\n"
