"<div data-oe-version=\"2.0\">Dear Sir or Madam,</div><div><br/></"
"div><div>Please find attached the CSV file containing all fiscal "
"attestations for the year <t t-out=\"object.invoice_date.year\">.</t></"
"div><br/><div>If you require any additional information, feel free to reach "
